who is the President of the
Sealaska Heritage Institute,

00:16:36.250 --> 00:16:41.300
who is the author of many,
many writings and publications,

00:16:41.300 --> 00:16:44.480
among them Indigenous Value:
Strengthening Resiliency

00:16:44.480 --> 00:16:48.740
