01:23:48.240 --> 01:23:51.630
We need different models
of democratic institutions

01:23:51.630 --> 01:23:55.440
and of collective
action that can create

01:23:55.440 --> 01:23:56.940
the types of
inclusive empowerment

01:23:56.940 --> 01:23:58.920
that respond to these
other types of control.

01:23:58.920 --> 01:24:02.280
And so it's this constant
experimentation, if you will,

01:24:02.280 --> 01:24:04.830
about different vehicles
for collective action

01:24:04.830 --> 01:24:08.310
that aren't just the
formal voting franchise,

01:24:08.310 --> 01:24:10.960
but extend to other
domains as well.

